========== 02/15/18 ==========
==============================

I) === Summary ===
	A) Created Settings Activity
	B) Navigated From Homepage to Settings Page
	C) Fixed up button in action bar to return to Homepage activity
	D) Customized Some Settings

II) === Takeaways: ===
	- dp = pixel density
	- sp = scaled pixel density
		- good for making textSize relative to device Text Size settings

III) === Resources: ===
	- ANDROID TASK MAKER APP 3 (Detail Activity, Settings Activity) by Delaroy Studios
		- https://youtu.be/jDBZWz6ALUk

	- Providing Up Navigation
		- https://developer.android.com/training/implementing-navigation/ancestral.html

	- Add Custom Menu Items to ActionBar with Settings MENU (Toolbar) by TechBrah
		- https://youtu.be/wzomye19mfU

	- Fixing the up button: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36250288/settings-activity-up-button


III) === Log: ===

A) Created Settings Activity
	- file > new > Activity > Settings Activity
	- Set as hierarchical parent after the fact
		- Providing Up Navigation: https://developer.android.com/training/implementing-navigation/ancestral.html
		- add `android:parentActivityName=".Homepage"` to AndroidManifest.xml
		- Edit onOptionsItemSelected()... case android.R.id.home
			- `super.onBackPressed();` instead of `startActivity(new Intent(getActivity(), SettingsActivity.class));`

B) Navigated From Homepage to Settings Page
	- https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36250288/settings-activity-up-button

C) up button in action bar not returning to Homepage activity
	- Create new listener and call finish()
		`
		@Override
	    public boolean onOptionsItemSelected(MenuItem item) {
	        int id = item.getItemId();
	        if (id == android.R.id.home) {
	             finish();
	             return true;
	        }
	        return super.onOptionsItemSelected(item);
	    }
	    `

D) Customized Some Settings
	- changed a setting to "Allow Notifications"
	- Added another list to Subscribe
		- Created list in strings.xml
		- Should use MultiSelectListPreference
	- Added subscribe as a dependency of allowing
	- Removed something from Data & Sync

E) Edited SideNavigation background gradient
	- res > drawable > side_nav_bar.xml

